## Streaming API

The `/v1/chat/completions` endpoint supports Server-Sent Events (SSE) for real-time token streaming.

```bash
curl -N http://localhost:8080/v1/chat/completions \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "model": "llama3-8b",
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Hello"}],
    "stream": true
  }'
```

